    <h1 class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-900 sm:text-3xl mb-4">Policy on Ethical Sourcing of Food and Supplies</h1>
    <div class="prose prose-slate max-w-none">
      <p><strong>Policy Title:</strong> Policy on Ethical Sourcing of Food and Supplies (PESFS)</p>
      <p><strong>Policy Number:</strong> ST-PO-6AF</p>
      <p><strong>Date Created:</strong> 15-09-2023</p>
      <p><strong>Responsible:</strong> Chief Operational Officer</p>
